Package: MARVEL
Title: Revealing Splicing Dynamics at Single-Cell Resolution
Version: 2.0.5
Description: Alternative splicing represents an additional and underappreciated layer of complexity underlying gene expression profiles. Nevertheless, there remains hitherto a paucity of software to investigate splicing dynamics at single-cell resolution. 'MARVEL' enables splicing analysis of RNA-sequencing data generated from plate- and droplet-based library preparation methods.
